General.Name: Juno Minerals Ltd
General.Description: Juno Minerals Limited, an independent mining company, engages in the evaluation and development of iron ore properties in Australia. It holds interests in the Central Yilgarn Iron Project, which consists of the Mount Mason DSO hematite and Mount Ida magnetite project located in the Yilgarn region of Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Perth, Australia.
